     H            Y.
     F** AJVRDL **********************************
     F*    SAIHENSEI AJVPPLG                     *
     F*                                          *
     F*       Y.SAMEJIMA     2015.06.04          *
     F********************************** AJVRDL **
     FAJVPPLG UF  E                    DISK
     I*
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80LGDTHZ
     I                                        1   40LGDTYY
     I                                        5   60LGDTMM
     I                                        7   80LGDTDD
     I*
     C*DELETE FROM MINUS 90 DAYS
     C                     MOVEL*DATE     PDATE
     C                     MOVEL'-'       PPORM
     C                     MOVEL'0090'    PDAYS
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PRDAT
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PRTN
     C*
     C                     CALL 'DATR12'
     C                     PARM           PDATE   8
     C                     PARM           PPORM   1        + OR -
     C                     PARM           PDAYS   4
     C                     PARM           PRDAT   8
     C                     PARM           PRTN    1
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD0         ##DAT   80
     C                     MOVELPRDAT     ##DAT
     C*
     C           1         SETLLAJVPPLG
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ AJVPPLG                  99
     C   99                LEAVE
     C           LGDTHZ    IFLE ##DAT
     C                     DELETAJVPPLG
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
